<li>When <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=ssh&amp;sektion=1">ssh(1)</a> is reading a password, don't panic if <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=fork&amp;sektion=2">fork(2)</a> or <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=pipe&amp;sektion=2">pipe(2)</a> fail; just return an empty password.
